        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, deep pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 5-6 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> ginger</strong> and <strong>sliced mushrooms </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
