            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail, peel and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Drain the <strong>tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Cut the <strong>tofu</strong> into cubes</p><p>Dissolve the<strong> miso paste</strong>, <strong>gochujang paste</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>toasted sesame oil</strong> and the <strong>soy sauce </strong>with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>in 550ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [950ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your <strong>jjigae stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
