    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Korean-style tofu jjigae stew </strong>and<strong> sticky rice</strong> in separate bowls</p><p>Garnish the stew with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Tip: Add your rice into the stew or eat the stew with a spoonful of rice to absorb all of the broth!</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
